#sws-container.accountContainer
  button.close(type='button')
    span Close
  h2
    span Send with Style&nbsp;
    input#sws-enabled-check(type='checkbox')
    | &nbsp;
    label#sws-enabled-label(for='sws-enabled-check')
  p.explanation Type your text as you normally would, use the codes to style your text.
  table.sws-info-table
    tr
      th Code
      th Example
    tr
      td
        code %C
        | &nbsp;for&nbsp;
        a#sws-colors-anchor(title='Click here to show color numbers', style='border-bottom: 1px dashed black;')
          font(color='#ff0000') c
          font(color='#cc8f33') o
          font(color='#99ed66') l
          font(color='#66f899') o
          font(color='#33accc') r
      td
        code %C2This is blue
        |  → 
        code
          span(style='color: blue') This is blue
    tr#sws-colors-box
      td(colspan='2')
        span.sws-little-box.bg-white.black 0
        span.sws-little-box.bg-black.white 1
        span.sws-little-box.bg-navy.white 2
        span.sws-little-box.bg-green.white 3
        span.sws-little-box.bg-red.black 4
        span.sws-little-box.bg-maroon.white 5
        span.sws-little-box.bg-purple.white 6
        span.sws-little-box.bg-orange.black 7
        span.sws-little-box.bg-yellow.black 8
        span.sws-little-box.bg-lime.black 9
        span.sws-little-box.bg-teal.white 10
        span.sws-little-box.bg-cyan.black 11
        span.sws-little-box.bg-blue.white 12
        span.sws-little-box.bg-magenta.black 13
        span.sws-little-box.bg-grey.black 14
        span.sws-little-box.bg-silver.black 15
    tr
      td
        code %B
        |  for 
        b bold
      td
        code %BVery bold
        |  → 
        code
          b Very bold
    tr
      td
        code %I
        |  for 
        i italic
      td
        code %IPizza
        |  → 
        code
          i Pizza
    tr
      td
        code %U
        |  for 
        u underline
      td
        code %UBeep
        |  → 
        code
          u Beep
    tr
      td
        code %R
        |  for reset
      td
        code %C4Wo%Rrd
        |  → 
        code
          span(style='color: red') Wo
          | rd
  p.explanation
    | Custom aliases (
    a(href='https://github.com/dogancelik/irccloud-sws#custom-aliases-examples', target='_blank') ?
    | )
  textarea#sws-custom-alias
  p#sws-donate.explanation
    | If you like this script, please 
    a(href='https://flattr.com/submit/auto?user_id=dogancelik&url=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fdogancelik%2Firccloud-sws', target='_blank')
      img(border='0', src='//api.flattr.com/button/flattr-badge-large.png', alt='Flattr this', title='Flattr this')
    | &nbsp;or help me via&nbsp;
    a(href='https://gratipay.com/dogancelik/', target='_blank') Gratipay
  p.explanation
    a(href='https://github.com/dogancelik/irccloud-sws', target='_blank') Source code